E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Good Guy Fluctuation: Leonard doubts his feelings for Priya when he kisses a woman he meets in the comic book shop. The gang pull pranks on Sheldon to celebrate Halloween. (S5 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Isolation Permutation: Amy is heartbroken when she finds out that Penny and Bernadette went on a shopping trip to buy bridesmaids' dresses without her. (S5 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Ornithophobia Diffusion: Leonard and Penny attempt to spend time together as friends without anybody else around, while Sheldon faces his fear of birds. (S5 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Tale of Two Springfields: When class rivalries split Springfield in two, Homer becomes mayor of 'New Springfield'. (S12 Ep2/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lisa the Tree Hugger: A dramatic rooftop protest at Krusty Burger inspires Lisa to become an eco-radical - especially when she sees how cute one of the protestors is... (S12 Ep4/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Theresa risks her own safety to help a spiralling Mercedes. And a resident worries about what a scorned ex is capable of...

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: I Love Lisa: On Valentine's Day, Lisa takes pity on Ralph and gives him a card. But when he falls in love with her, it leads to a bitter feud between their families. (S4 Ep15/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Celebrity Bake Off...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...for Stand Up To Cancer: Oti Mabuse, Gabby Logan, David O'Doherty and Suzi Ruffell make ice cream rolls, a kids' party favourite and their biggest fear in meringue form.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Anna Richardson hosts the daring dating show as student Charles hopes to turn his disastrous love life around, while non-binary pansexual Lee is open to all genders. (S4 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proton Displacement: Sheldon is jealous when Professor Proton asks Leonard to read his latest publication, so he befriends a TV personality from a rival science show. (S7 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Itchy Brain Simulation: Leonard worries that Sheldon will overreact when he confesses that he failed to return a DVD to the rental shop seven years earlier. (S7 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lyn has a surprise for her date Steve: she's pregnant. Can Rebecca see past Freddie's nerves? Cindy and Elan, who have matching outfits, bond over matters of the heart and family. (S10 Ep2) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Tale of Two Springfields: When class rivalries split Springfield in two, Homer becomes mayor of 'New Springfield'. (S12 Ep2/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Family Dynamics and a Red Fiero: Sheldon must study the dynamics of his family for his school psychology project. George Sr is offered a new job in Oklahoma. (S2 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Stunted Childhood and a Can of Fancy Mixed Nuts: Sheldon experiments with practical jokes. Meemaw teaches Dr Sturgis to drive, which tests their relationship. (S2 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Yes-Woman: To be less negative, Claire rebrands herself as the woman who says 'yes', and inadvertently approves of Luke's new relationship with a colleague. (S10 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Age of Darkness: The family rally round to comfort Erica when she's dumped by her boyfriend Drew. Barry becomes addicted to an arcade video game. (S1 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Wrestler Named Goldberg: Murray coaches Barry for his first high school wrestling match but keeps it a secret from Beverly, who is sure to disapprove. (S1 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Jungle: When a mountain lion gets loose in the neighbourhood, the Butlers and Johnsons must shelter together, which leads to unexpected revelations. (S5 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Milestone: Calvin struggles to find a birthday gift for Tina. Gemma tries to get some VIP tickets, through a connection to actor Jerry O'Connell. (S5 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proton Displacement: Sheldon is jealous when Professor Proton asks Leonard to read his latest publication, so he befriends a TV personality from a rival science show. (S7 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Theresa risks her own safety to help a spiralling Mercedes. And a resident worries about what a scorned ex is capable of...

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Other Smother: While attempting to micro-manage Barry and Erica's search for college places, Beverly is pitted against a rival meddling mother. (S1 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: You Opened the Door: Adam reluctantly agrees to take dancing lessons from Beverly because he is planning to attend the school dance with Dana. (S1 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: D'oh Canada: Lisa goes to Canada and refuses to leave. Marge desperately tries to get her back. (S30 Ep21/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Crystal Blue-Haired Persuasion: Marge sells crystals and makes a fortune. Bart's grades take a mysterious turn for the better. (S30 Ep23/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Comic-Con Conundrum: Cut off from his father's fortune, Raj appoints Sheldon to organise his finances. Penny considers joining the guys at Comic-Con. (S10 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Escape Hatch Identification: Leonard and Penny offer Sheldon's old room to Raj when he's forced to move out of his flat, leading to unexpected conflict. (S10 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Patriot Games: Alex faces her worst nightmare: having to share the Valedictorian title with her number one competitor, Sunjay. (S6 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
